The funeral of a former governor of Kano State and Minister of Federal Capital Territory (FCT), Air Vice Marshal, Hamza Abdullahi (rtd), is expected to be conducted at the palace of Emir of Hadejia in Jigawa State. This was disclosed, on Thursday, by the spokesperson of Hadejia Emirate, Mohammed Garba Talaki, while speaking with Daily Trust on phone. He said the remain of late AVM, Abdullahi, who died on Wednesday in Germany, is expected to arrive the country as soon as all formalities were completed. According to him, the deceased died after a brief illness. Ex- FCT minister, Hamza Abdullahi dies at the age 73 Former FCT minister,Hamza Abdullahi,dies at 76 Emir of Katagum dies at 89